## 2. API Endpoints Reference

The backend exposes **44 clean, secure REST endpoints** divided into 9 logical modules.

### A. Authentication & Session Module (`ApiAuthController`)
* `POST /api/v1/auth/login` - Public login supporting multi-field lookup (Email, Phone, or Username). Returns a Sanctum Token, user info, and configuration parameters.
* `POST /api/v1/auth/logout` - Revokes current authentication token.
* `GET /api/v1/auth/me` - Fetches profile details of the logged-in user.
* `PUT /api/v1/auth/profile` - Modifies profile details.
* `PUT /api/v1/auth/password` - Updates account password.

### B. User Management (`ApiUserController`)
* `GET /api/v1/users` - Fetches list of users (filtered by user type).
* `POST /api/v1/users` - Admits new user (Admins, Accountants, Librarians, Parents).
* `GET /api/v1/users/{id}` - Details of a specific user.
* `PUT /api/v1/users/{id}` - Modifies a user.
* `DELETE /api/v1/users/{id}` - Soft-deletes a user.
* `POST /api/v1/users/{id}/reset-password` - Resets a user's password to default.
* `POST /api/v1/users/block-state` - Blocks or unblocks a user.

### C. Student Admissions & Promotions (`ApiStudentController`)
* `GET /api/v1/students` - Retrieves student lists (optionally filtered by class).
* `POST /api/v1/students` - Processes student admission and auto-generates credentials.
* `GET /api/v1/students/{id}` - Detailed student academic and demographic profile.
* `PUT /api/v1/students/{id}` - Modifies student records.
* `DELETE /api/v1/students/{id}` - Deletes student record.
* `POST /api/v1/students/block-class` - Blocks or unblocks all students of a class.

### D. Academics Metadata (`ApiClassSectionSubjectController`)
* `GET /api/v1/classes` - List of all classes.
* `GET /api/v1/sections/{class_id}` - Sections belonging to a class.
* `GET /api/v1/subjects/{class_id}` - Subjects registered under a class.

### E. Gradebooks & Examinations (`ApiMarkAssessmentController`)
* `GET /api/v1/exams` - Lists all examinations.
* `GET /api/v1/marks/manage/{exam_id}/{class_id}/{subject_id}/{section_id?}` - Loads gradebook student marks list for inputting grades.
* `POST /api/v1/marks/update` - Bulk updates marks, averages, positions class-wise and section-wise.
* `GET /api/v1/tabulation/{exam_id}/{class_id}/{section_id}/{year}` - Computes term tabulation sheet.

### F. Fee Payments & Billing (`ApiPaymentController`)
* `GET /api/v1/payments` - Retrieves billing records and fee history.
* `GET /api/v1/payments/invoice/{student_id}/{year?}` - Fetches invoice lists (split by cleared and uncleared fees).
* `POST /api/v1/payments/pay/{pr_id}` - Registers fee payments, creates a receipt record, and dispatches SMS/email notifications to parents.
* `GET /api/v1/payments/receipt/{pr_id}` - Details of receipt logs.

### G. Messaging & Chat Platform (`ApiMessageController`)
* `GET /api/v1/messages` - Gets conversation threads.
* `GET /api/v1/messages/{id}` - Retrieves individual messages in a thread.
* `POST /api/v1/messages` - Creates a conversation thread.
* `POST /api/v1/messages/{id}/reply` - Appends a reply.

### H. Support Tickets (`ApiTicketController`)
* `GET /api/v1/tickets` - List of support tickets.
* `POST /api/v1/tickets` - Opens a support request.
* `GET /api/v1/tickets/{id}` - Detailed ticket history.
* `POST /api/v1/tickets/{id}/reply` - Appends a client message.
* `POST /api/v1/tickets/{id}/close` - Marks ticket as closed.

### I. Common Utility Lookups (`ApiUtilityController`)
* `GET /api/v1/utilities/nationalities` - All nationalities.
* `GET /api/v1/utilities/states/{nal_id}` - States in a nationality.
* `GET /api/v1/utilities/lgas/{state_id}` - LGAs in a state.
* `GET /api/v1/utilities/class-students/{class_id}` - Simple student lookups.
* `GET /api/v1/utilities/class-subjects/{class_id}` - Simple subject lookups.

